---
title: Carb Smart Lemongrass Turkey Meatballs with Creamy Lime Sauce and Asian-Style Slaw
description: Vietnamese food is typically fresh and vibrant, and this carb-smart meal is no exception! Tender turkey meatballs flavoured with lemongrass are stars of the show. A crunchy Asian-style coleslaw with baby spinach and a fragrant, umami-rich dressing, featuring punchy fish sauce, is the perfect side to transport you to paradise!
